    • Method Detail

      • uiReadyTripSegment

        public static TripSegmentBuilder uiReadyTripSegment()
        Creates a ui ready trip segment builder with the following field set:
        • TripIncident - if this builder is used via the withTripSegment() method of a trip incident builder, then use the incident created by the builder. Otherwise create a new ui ready trip incident.
        • TransportType - set to one of the valid transport types
        • SegmentCancelOnly - set to false
        Returns:
        a new trip segment builder
